  <div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Uploading your story</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <main>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6 text-gray-800 font-medium">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Prepare Your file</h2>
        <p>Ensure your file is saved in a supported format (e.g., <b>.mp4</b>, <b>.mp3</b>, or <b>.png</b>). <b>Story</b> supports video, audio, and images and we are planning on supporting plain text formats in the future.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Create an Account or Log In</h2>
        <p>You need to be signed in to upload to <b>Story</b>. Use the <a href="/auth/login" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">login</a> button at the top right of the screen. New users can <a href="/auth/register" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">register</a> with an <b>email</b>, <b>username</b> and <b>password</b>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Start uploading</h2>
        <p>Navigate to the upload page using the <a href="/upload" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">upload</a> button at the top of the screen, or the <svg class="-ml-0.5 size-5 inline-block" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon">
          <path d="M10.75 4.75a.75.75 0 0 0-1.5 0v4.5h-4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5h4.5v4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0v-4.5h4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 0-1.5h-4.5v-4.5Z"></path>
        </svg> if you are on mobile.
        <br>
        Once there, you'll be prompted to add a <b>title</b>, <b>description</b>, <b>date</b> and any <b>tags</b> that describe your story. This helps readers find and enjoy your work. You may also set a <b>privacy</b> value to make your story public or private.
        <br>
        <b>NOTE:</b> The <b>date</b> field is intended for when the <b>file itself</b> was created and not when it was uploaded.  If you are unsure of the date, then leave this field blank.
      </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Upload Your File</h2>
        <p>Navigate to the <a href="/upload" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Upload</a> page. Click "Choose File" to select your story from your device. After selecting, click the "Upload" button to start. <b>Do not</b> navigate away from the upload page until you get the confirmation that the upload has completed.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Submit and Share</h2>
        <p>After reviewing everything, click "Submit." Your story will now be live on the platform and accessible via your the <a href="/search-media" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline ">search-media</a> page. Share the link with your audience!</p>
      </section>

